news.title: China property shares extends gains after government highlights clearing inventory
news.para: The Hang Seng Mainland Properties Index rose 4% in the morning session to a more than four-month high, with China Vanke and Longfor Group jumping 10% and 7.8%, respectively.

news.title: No attachment of properties under PMLA after acquittal in scheduled offence: Delhi HC
news.para: The Delhi High Court has held that no proceedings under the Prevention of Money Laundering Act (PMLA), including attachment of properties, can continue after the accused is acquitted in the predicate offence even if an appeal against it is pending.

news.title: New condo in Mumbai's old neighbourhood combo deal commands highest price
news.para: In Mumbai, the real estate landscape is evolving with a shift towards modern amenities in new luxury condos. High prices in prime locations like Carmichael Road and Walkeshwar Road reflect the demand for upscale living in the city.
